title: [Ta'Vaalor, Victory Bridge]
description: Gracefully arcing above the murky depths of the Mistydeep River, the bridge's limestone blocks are so tightly fitted that seams are nearly invisible.  Thick bunches of rushes crowd the riverbank, as the chirping and whirring of insects hums through the air.
